{"tid":860081,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"不論男女都喜歡她！「民選港姐」朱千雪4大女生必學迷人特質","createTime":"2018-10-13T05:17:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T03:47:44.000Z","uid":9573,"like":50,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8bd4efe76ed4a3831d28dc0f0e1d8228fbb4f4fe","tid":860081,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T05:17:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/lQeskyUJlzipO65Jq.7KWQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NTAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/she_com_523/6763b565856a716e49ba855d6125a8ab\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FlQeskyUJlzipO65Jq.7KWQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NTAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fshe_com_523%2F6763b565856a716e49ba855d6125a8ab&h=5d718317&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨有有傳「民選港姐」朱千雪已加入了一間位於金鐘嘅top 5著名律師行，並將會退出娛樂圈，正式投身法律界做「Law界女神」！其實朱千雪不論在演藝事業上，還是人生規劃上都有多地方值得我們學習！<br />\n<br />\n1) 儉樸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/8oWQAJNqXGbK28HKYeCklA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NTAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/she_com_523/f4b54748ea37e44ec9655a1b121fdddd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F8oWQAJNqXGbK28HKYeCklA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NTAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fshe_com_523%2Ff4b54748ea37e44ec9655a1b121fdddd&h=60e7938d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n朱千雪縱然是港姐出生，私底下生活亦都相當檢樸，一點明星架子也沒有！日常衣著也是簡簡單單的，沒有半點名牌，出入工作都只會乘坐公共交通公共 ，跟普羅大眾無異。宏觀一下娛樂圈，試問有哪個女星能做到這一點？應該説就算普通女生也難以做到如此儉樸！<br />\n<br />\n2) 不亂搞男女關係<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/bDFMdKi7ODzgERzQpE0uyw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NTAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/she_com_523/9e084f213c6d601fec16149c92f1ba02\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FbDFMdKi7ODzgERzQpE0uyw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NTAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fshe_com_523%2F9e084f213c6d601fec16149c92f1ba02&h=e131fc03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n朱千雪一直以來都與不少男星合作拍劇，但從來都沒有試過和任何一個傳出緋聞，屬娛樂圈鮮有的零緋聞女星。就算拍住緋聞多多的王浩信，亦能獨善其身。當一個女生面對誘惑時，仍能拒絕以及堅持自己，這也算是一種迷人的特質啊！<br />\n<br />\n3）清楚自己目標<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/8121hgQu6YOKGhytfQLFKQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NTAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/she_com_523/3bbb8144e09a9896f977b3387fc7ff90\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F8121hgQu6YOKGhytfQLFKQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NTAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fshe_com_523%2F3bbb8144e09a9896f977b3387fc7ff90&h=f5abdd5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n站在名和利之前，很多女生久而久之便會迷失了自己，忘記自己的目標，但朱千雪並不是這一種女生！朱千雪浸淫在娛樂圈之個大染缸，卻沒有留戀名利和獎項，在事業的顛峯時期毅然去進修法律和法律傳播，最後更成功以碩士畢業，實屬不少女生的典範。<br />\n<br />\n4）懂得理財投資<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/TMfOjmv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FTMfOjmv.jpg&h=d42bbbe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n朱千雪現擁有兩個市值約一千萬的單位，一個是她現居住的小西灣藍灣半島高層單位，另一物業則在愉景灣。雖然有做五金生意的父蔭幫助，但朱千雪靠著自己的拍劇以及廣告收入，妥善地理財，進行投資，現在也算是圈中的小富婆。"},{"pid":"716e44d0638f2dab45e843b8cb6aaf538fe1e425","tid":860081,"uid":21204,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T05:34:10.000Z","msg":"正評比雲爺爺"},{"pid":"8ec8bbb5d3475110b2289ce10d0f73fa2aef2c42","tid":860081,"uid":153497,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T06:42:02.000Z","msg":"雲爺爺梗係識投資啦，賣走哂啲球員<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19cd8b0fa219c9ef5b79cd2a3568200c2c392275","tid":860081,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T00:31:21.000Z","msg":"嫁埋金雞<br />\n<br />\n人生贏家"},{"pid":"852e86612af7c596aa4f5bbd965e433b294d2ae2","tid":860081,"uid":57410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T02:09:39.000Z","msg":"巨浪 卷起朱千雪"},{"pid":"7847e228c284e18ff805ce7fabdb3c83f0af8bec","tid":860081,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"716e44d0638f2dab45e843b8cb6aaf538fe1e425","tid":860081,"uid":21204,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T05:34:10.000Z","msg":"正評比雲爺爺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T03:10:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f8e0b03f3191ca0d73152b680679f1a22374610","tid":860081,"uid":140831,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T03:14:51.000Z","msg":"咪又係靠老豆+好彩出世有個靚樣 <br />\n仲要講撚到幾辛苦幾咁努力 收皮啦"},{"pid":"21d49f1e581aad90f0d343236c1789db86f21b0c","tid":860081,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f8e0b03f3191ca0d73152b680679f1a22374610","tid":860081,"uid":140831,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T03:14:51.000Z","msg":"咪又係靠老豆+好彩出世有個靚樣 <br />\n仲要講撚到幾辛苦幾咁努力 收皮啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T03:19:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/14/111920_2cfcd0b256c0f1b316169697a9b5e49f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F14%2F111920_2cfcd0b256c0f1b316169697a9b5e49f.png&h=9033eae3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"874ba35dce768882995fabc6a22175be74286d60","tid":860081,"uid":36283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T03:29:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/14/112935_954d55c5dc83c68ddda7b49da3b29855.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F14%2F112935_954d55c5dc83c68ddda7b49da3b29855.png&h=bdaaf51e&s={SIZE}\" />不知幾親民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0d5e638bd402b38616940509e36d6bdce49ae91","tid":860081,"uid":2